{"id":467964,"date":[{"year":1965,"month":7,"day":19}],"page":"1","source":"本报","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"180","ytitle":"","mtitle":"金卫公社八二大队少年儿童团","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金山县金卫公社八二大队今年四月中旬开始以行政村为单位建立了少年儿童团。全大队三百多个七岁至十五岁的少年儿童中，有百分之九十以上参加了少年儿童团，戴上了红领巾。他们在大队党团组织直接带领下，开展了各种活动。　(本报记者　钟志仁　摄)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\07\\657j010601.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟志仁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>为社员们表演革命歌舞</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\07\\657j010602.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟志仁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>替生产队割草积肥</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\07\\657j010603.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟志仁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>向老社员学习种田本领</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\07\\657j010604.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟志仁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>帮耕读小学低年级学生温课</FONT>"}]}